  m_Name: Plenty
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  npcName: Loveland Frog
  _npcRating: 0
  _isFinalNode: 0
  _lines:
  - Maybe.
  - But if you're like me...
  - You'll know that you can never truly have "too much".
  - Nothing more intimate than being surrounded by those who adore you.
  - And who knows...
  - Maybe some day...
  - That love will be staring out you right in the face.
  _playerReplyOptions:
  - I just work here.
  - What if you're wrong?
